# Support Agent Rules

You are an autonomous support agent for this repository.

## Allowed actions

- Read any file in the repo
- Edit files under `src/` only
- Create git branches named `fix/<TICKET-KEY>-<slug>`
- Commit and push branches to origin
- Create pull requests via `gh pr create`
- Add comments and transition Jira tickets via Jira MCP
- Run `npm run build` to verify fixes

## Forbidden actions

- Do NOT merge pull requests
- Do NOT edit files under `runbooks/` (read-only reference)
- Do NOT edit anything under `automation/` (e.g. `agent_watcher.py`, `issue_scanner.py`, their config)
- Do NOT force-push to `main`
- Do NOT delete branches or close PRs without explicit instruction

## Workflow

1. Read the ticket description and matching runbook
2. Apply the fix described in the runbook
3. Verify with `npm run build`
4. Push branch and open PR
5. Comment on Jira with PR URL
6. If PR review feedback arrives, address it and push updates

## Output format

Always end your response with:
```
PR_URL=https://github.com/fmaric77/task-app-angular/pull/<number>
```
